r%20a%20company%20to%20raise%20capital%20by%20offering%20existing%20shareholders%20the%20opportunity%20to%20buy%20additional%20shares%20at%20a%20discounted%20price%2C%20typically%20in%20proportion%20to%20their%20existing%20holdings.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EByju%E2%80%99s%20rights%20issue%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20priced%20at%20a%2099%25%20cut%20to%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20previous%20peak%20valuation%20of%20%2422%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20such%20a%20low%20price%2C%20if%20existing%20shareholders%20do%20not%20participate%20in%20the%20rights%20issue%2C%20they%20will%20see%20their%20ownership%20stake%20in%20the%20company%20diluted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20investors%20like%20Prosus%20and%20Peak%20XV%20need%20to%20pump%20in%20%2418%20million%20and%20%2414%20million%2C%20respectively%2C%20or%20they%20will%20virtually%20see%20their%20holding%20wiped%20off%2C%20the%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Ftech%2Fstartups%2Fbyjus-shareholder-group-calls-for-egm-to-vote-for-ouster-of-byju-raveendran-board%2Farticleshow%2F107326462.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%20Economic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20EGM%2C%20the%20shareholders%20will%20vote%20to%20oust%20Byju%E2%80%99s%20CEO%20Raveendran%20and%20his%20family%20members%20from%20the%20board%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20restrain%20them%20from%20running%20the%20operations%20at%20the%20edtech%20startup%2C%20people%20in%20the%20know%20told%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaveendran%20and%20family%20own%20about%2026%25%20in%20the%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20deeply%20concerned%20about%20the%20future%20stability%20of%20the%20company%20under%20its%20current%20leadership%20and%20with%20the%20constitution%20of%20the%20board%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20investors%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20any%20resolution%20to%20pass%20at%20the%20EGM%2C%20it%20will%20need%20to%20muster%20support%20of%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20shareholders.%3C%2