nterim%20budget%20is%20a%20guideline%20for%20us.%20I%20am%20hopeful%20that%20the%20country%20will%20touch%20new%20heights%20of%20prosperity.%20Development%20for%20everyone%20is%20taking%20place.%20This%20journey%20will%20continue%20with%20your%20blessings.%20Ram%20Ram.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20this%20is%20not%20a%20full%20budget%2C%20taxpayers%20had%20hoped%20for%20some%20relief%20in%20an%20election%20year.%20There%20was%20buzz%20on%20the%20possibility%20of%20the%20government%20revising%20the%20cap%20on%20investment%20exempted%20from%20Income%20Tax.%20Some%20Opposition%20leaders%20had%20also%20expected%20the%20government%20to%20make%20populist%20announcements%20with%20its%20eye%20on%20the%20elections.%20But%20what%20was%20presented%20was%20a%20statement%20of%20confidence%20and%20a%20plan%20to%20keep%20the%20big%20announcements%20for%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20said%20she%20had%20decided%20to%20not%20make%20any%20taxation%20changes%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20convention%20in%20interim%20budgets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20welcomed%20the%20budget.%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20it%20%26quot%3Bdraws%20the%20roadmap%26quot%3B%20to%20achieve%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20vision%20of%20a%20Developed%20Bharat%20by%202047.%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%20Dr%20S%20Jaishankar%20said%20the%20budget%20%26quot%3Bcaptures%20a%20decade%20of%20transformation%2C%20while%20laying%20out%20a%20vision%20of%20further%20development%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Minister%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekar%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%20that%20it%20is%20an%20%26quot%3Bexcellent%20summary%20of%20the%20qualitative%20and%20quantitative%20transformation%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%26quot%3B.%20Union%20Minister%20and%20BJP%20veteran%20Nitin%20Gadkari%20said%20%26quot%3Bthis%20is%20a%20budget%20to%20speed%20up%20country's%20development%20and%20increase%20employment%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOpposition%