at%20she%20doesn't%20even%20live%20there.%20%26quot%3BThe%20relevant%20Residents'%20Welfare%20Association%20is%20from%20a%20colony%20where%20I%20do%20not%20live!%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20a%20Facebook%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20residents'%20welfare%20association%20in%20Jangpura%2C%20in%20a%20letter%2C%20asked%20Mr%20Aiyar%20and%20her%20daughter%20to%20leave%20the%20colony.%20In%20the%20letter%2C%20the%20RWA%20president%20said%20the%20association%20was%20approached%20by%20residents%20of%20the%20colony%20over%20her%20social%20media%20%26quot%3Bstand%2Frant%26quot%3B%20against%20the%20consecration%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RWA%20accused%20Suranya%20of%20%26quot%3Bhate%20speech%26quot%3B%20and%20requested%20her%20to%20follow%20the%20norms%20of%20a%20good%20citizen.%20It%20claimed%20the%20colony%20was%20inhabited%20by%20residents%20who%20came%20to%20India%20from%20Pakistan%20after%20partition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20erupted%20when%20the%2049-year-old%2C%20in%20a%20Facebook%20post%20on%20January%2020%2C%20had%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20fasting%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20'pran%20pratishtha'%20ceremony%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%20She%20said%20it%20was%20an%20expression%20of%20love%20and%20sorrow%20for%20fellow%20Muslim%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20Ms%20Aiyar%20said%20through%20social%20media%20was%20unbecoming%20of%20an%20educated%20person%2C%20who%20should%20have%20understood%20that%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20was%20being%20built%20after%20500%20years%20and%20that%20too%20after%205-0%20Supreme%20Court%20verdict%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RWA%20responded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20RWA%20notice%2C%20she%20said%20the%20reasons%20for%20her%20disagreement%20were%20expressed%20by%20her%20in%20a%20previous%20speech%20(video)%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20made%20a%20spiritual%20presentation%20of%20my%20own%20pain%20about%20this%20by%20fasting%20peacefully%20in%20my%20home%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20matters%20is%20that%20whatever%20point%20of%20view%20we%20put%20forward%2C%20whether%20people%20can%20see%20some%20sense%20in%20it.%20And%20if%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20this%20process%2C%20in%20India%2C%20we%20can%20even%20just%20find%20a%20more%20civilised%2C%20a%20more%20thinking%20and%20a%20more%20sincere%20way%20of%20talking%20and%20feeling%20about%20these%20things%2C%20then%20we%20would%20have%20achieved%20something%20(sic)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20stressing%20that%20she%20studied%20abroad%20and%20was%20involved%20with%20activism%20with%20people%20of%20all%20political%20background.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20development%2C%20the%20BJP%20said%20the%20action%20of%20the%20RWA%20should%20serve%20as%20a%20message%20to%20everyone%20who%20believes%20abusing%20Hindu%20beliefs%20is%20%26quot%3Bpar%20for%20the%20course%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RWA%20has%20%26quot%3Basked%20Congress%20leader%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20and%20his%20daughter%20to%20apologise%20for%20defiling%20the%20Pran%20Pratistha%20ceremony%20at%20Ram%20Mandir%2C%20and%20leave%20the%20residential%20colony%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20IT%20department%20head%20Amit%20Malviya%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMani%20Shankar%20Aiyar%20is%20yet%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20row.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20'pran%20pratishtha'%20or%20consecration%20ceremony%20of%20Ram%20Lalla%20-%20headlined%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20-%20was%20held%20at%20the%20newly%20built%20Ram%20temple%20in%20Ayodhya%20on%20January%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706767440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fe0l77j5o_suranya-aiyar-facebook_625x300_01_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmani-shankar-aiyars-daughter-on-move-out-notice-by-delhi-colony-over-ram-temple-i-dont-live-there-4971691%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Senior%20Congress%20leader%20Mani%20Shankar%20Aiyar's%20daughter%20Suranya%20Aiyar%2C%20who%20was%20asked%20to%20vacate%20%26quot%3Btheir%26quot%3B%20house%20in%20south-east%20Delhi%20over%20her%20Ram%20Temple%20post%2C%20has%20said%20that%20she%20doesn't%20even%20live%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmani-shankar-aiyars-daughter-on-move-out-notice-by-delhi-colony-over-ram-temple-i-dont-live-there-4971691%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmani-shankar-aiyars-daughter-on-move-out-notice-by-delhi-colony-over-ram-temple-i-dont-live-there-4971691%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmani-shankar-aiyars-daughter-on-move-out-notice-by-delhi-colony-over-ram-temple-i-dont-live-there-4971691%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hindus%20Pray%20In%20Gyanvapi%20Cellar%2C%2030%20Years%20After%20Mulayam%20Yadav%20Sealed%20It%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMembers%20of%20a%20Hindu%20priests'%20family%20started%20praying%20at%20a%20cellar%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20Varanasi's%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20after%20a%20district%20court%20yesterday%20ordered%20the%20administration%20to%20unseal%20the%20premises%2C%2030%20years%20after%20it%20was%20sealed%20on%20the%20orders%20of%20former%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Mulayam%20Singh%20Yadav%2C%C2%A0shortly%20after%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20demolition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHindu%20side%20allowed%20to%20offer%20prayers...%20district%20administration%20will%20have%20to%20make%20arrangements%20in%20seven%20days.%20Everyone%20will%20have%20the%20right%20to%20pray%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20Vishnu%20Shankar%20Jain%2C%20lawyer%20for%20the%20Hindu%20side%2C%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20area%20near%20the%20mosque%2C%20located%20right%20next%20to%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20temple%2C%20witnessed%20frenetic%20activity%20late%20last%20night%20as%20Hindu%20devotees%20started%20reaching%20the%20mosque%20to%20pray%20in%20the%20cellar%2C%20named%20'Vyas%20ka%20tehkana'.%20Members%20of%20a%20Hindu%20outfit%2C%20Rashtriya%20Hindu%20Dal%2C%20were%20seen%20pasting%20the%20'mandir'%20(temple)%20word%20on%20a%20signage%20near%20the%20mosque.%20The%20puja%20started%20around%203%20am%20today.%20Heavy%20force%20has%20been%20deployed%20to%20prevent%20any%20untoward%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20has%20four%20cellars%20in%20its%20basement.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20in%20the%20possession%20of%20a%20family%20of%20priests%20that%20used%20to%20live%20there.%20Somnath%20Vyas%2C%20a%20member%20of%20Vyas%20family%2C%20offered%20prayers%20in%20the%20cellar%20before%20it%20was%20sealed%20in%201993%2C%20according%20to%20the%20petition%20by%20Shailendra%20Pathak%2C%20the%20petitioner%20and%20a%20member%20of%20the%20family.%20He%20had%20argued%20in%20court%20that%20as%20hereditary%20priests%2C%20they%20should%20be%20allowed%20to%20enter%20the%20structure%20and%20worship%20there.%20The%20court%20yesterday%20asked%20the%20district%20administration%20to%20ensure%20that%20prayers%20can%20be%20held%20inside%20the%20cellar%20within%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20mosque%20committee%20has%20said%20they%20would%20be%20challenging%20the%20court's%20order%20in%20Allahabad%20High%20Court.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20happening%20to%20get%20political%20advantage.%20The%20same%20approach%20is%20being%20adopted%2C%20which%20was%20done%20in%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20their%20counsel%20Merajuddin%20Siddiqui%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYesterday's%20order%20is%20being%20seen%20as%20a%20major%20development%20in%20the%20Gyanvapi%20case%2C%20in%20which%20Hindu%20petitioners%20have%20sought%20permission%20to%20pray%20in%20the%20mosque%20complex.%20The%20Archaeological%20Survey%20of%20India%2C%20which%20conducted%20a%20survey%20of%20the%20premises%2C%20has%20shared%20its%20report%20with%20the%20petitioners%20and%20the%20mosque%20committee.%20The%20report%20concluded%20that%20a%20large%20Hindu%20temple%20existed%20on%20the%20site%20before%20the%20mosque%20was%20built.%20Four%20Hindu%20women%20have%20now%20moved%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20seeking%20the%20excavation%20and%20scientific%20survey%20of%20a%20section%20that%20had%20been%20sealed%20by%20a%20court%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20has%20stressed%20that%20due%20process%20must%20be%20followed%20while%20implementing%20the%20court%20order.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Varanasi%20Court%20fixed%20a%207-day%20period%20for%20it.%20What%20we%20are%20seeing%20now%20is%20a%20concerted%20effort%20to%20go%20beyond%20the%20due%20process%20and%20prevent%20any%20legal%20recourse%20that%20can%20be%20taken%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20refrained%20from%20commenting%20on%20yesterday's%20development%2C%20saying%20the%20matter%20is%20subjudice.%20Hindu%20outfits%20such%20as%20the%20Vishva%20Hindu%20Parishad%20have%20welcomed%20the%20ruling.%20%26quot%3BToday%2C%20a%20court%20in%20Kashi%20has%20given%20a%20very%20important%20decision%2C%20filling%20the%20hearts%20of%20every%20Hindu%20with%20joy%2C%26quot%3B%20VHP%20working%20president%20Alok%20Kumar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706764020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fumrgb928_gyanvapi-mosque_625x300_01_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindus-pray-in-gyanvapi-mosque-cellar-30-years-after-mulayam-yadav-sealed-it-4971387%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Members%20of%20a%20Hindu%20priests'%20family%20started%20praying%20at%20a%20cellar%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20Varanasi's%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20after%20a%20district%20court%20yesterday%20ordered%20the%20administration%20to%20unseal%20the%20premises%2C%2030%20years%20after%20it%20was%20sealed%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhindus-pray-in-gyanvapi-mosque-cellar-30-years-after-mulayam-yadav-sealed-it-4971387%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What%20RBI%20Order%20Means%20For%20Paytm%20And%20Its%20Users%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndian%20regulators%20ordered%20the%20parent%20of%20digital-payments%20provider%20Paytm%20to%20halt%20a%20bulk%20of%20its%20business%2C%20dealing%20a%20severe%20blow%20to%20a%20high-profile%20tech%20pioneer%20that%20grappled%20for%20years%20with%20regulators%20and%20criticism%20around%20its%20Chinese%20backing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20on%20Wednesday%20ordered%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Ltd.%20to%20stop%20its%20popular%20mobile%20wallet%20business%20along%20with%20other%20activities%2C%20citing%20persistent%20non-compliance%20and%20supervisory%20concerns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20abrupt%20action%20suggests%20regulators%20have%20grown%20dissatisfied%20with%20the%20fintech%20pioneer%20and%20raises%20the%20prospect%20of%20more%20action%20down%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20is%20a%20major%20setback%20for%20charismatic%20founder%20Vijay%20Shekhar%20Sharma%2C%20just%20as%20he's%20trying%20to%20convince%20investors%20Paytm%20can%20reverse%20years%20of%20losses%20to%20become%20sustainably%20profitable.%20The%20ruling%20could%20directly%20and%20indirectly%20slash%20more%20than%20half%20of%20its%20earnings%2C%20Jefferies%20analysts%20estimated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%20hampers%20Paytm's%20ability%20to%20retain%20customers%20in%20its%20ecosystem%2C%20and%20accordingly%20restricts%20it%20from%20selling%20payment%20products%20and%20loan%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20Macquarie%20analysts%20including%20Suresh%20Ganapathy%20said%20in%20a%20note.%20%26quot%3BRevenue%20and%20profitability%20implications%20in%20the%20medium%20to%20long%20term%20could%20be%20significant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20regulator%20said%20the%20bank%20arm%2C%20which%20processes%20transactions%20for%20the%20giant%20payments%20brand%20Paytm%2C%20must%20stop%20its%20banking%20activities%20after%20February%2029.%20Existing%20customers%2C%20however%2C%20can%20withdraw%20their%20funds%20and%20use%20up%20the%20balance%20in%20the%20prepaid%20cards%20or%20wallets%20without%20any%20restrictions%2C%20the%20RBI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20could%20directly%20reduce%20Paytm's%20earnings%20before%20interest%2C%20taxes%2C%20depreciation%20and%20amortization%20by%20as%20much%20as%2030%25%20and%20indirectly%20by%20as%20my%20much%20as%2025%25%20because%20of%20impact%20to%20its%20reputation%2C%20Jefferies%20analysts%20said%20in%20a%20note.%20Jefferies%20cut%20its%20price%20target%20for%20Paytm%20shares%20to%20500%20rupees%20from%201%2C050%20rupees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoftBank%20Group%20Corp.-backed%20Paytm%2C%20whose%20official%20name%20is%20One97%20Communications%20Ltd.%2C%20went%20public%20to%20much%20fanfare%20in%20late%202021%20after%20Sharma%20built%20the%20company%20to%20make%20it%20easier%20for%20consumers%20to%20make%20payments%20and%20transfer%20money.%20Still%2C%20its%20stock%20has%20slumped%20more%20than%2060%25%20since%20as%20investors%20questioned%20its%20profit-making%20ability%20and%20it%20tussled%20with%20regulators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20order%20comes%20nearly%20two%20years%20after%20the%20regulator%20barred%20the%20bank%20from%20taking%20on%20new%20customers%20because%20it%20violated%20certain%20rules%2C%20Bloomberg%20News%20had%20reported.%20Sharma%20had%20then%20said%20the%20bank%20is%20fully%20compliant%20with%20Indian%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20had%20asked%20the%20bank%2C%20which%20operates%20under%20a%20restricted%20license%20that%20doesn't%20allow%20it%20to%20lend%20but%20accept%20deposits%20of%20as%20much%20as%20200%2C000%20rupees%20(%242%2C408)%20per%20account%2C%20to%20stop%20onboarding%20customers%20pending%20an%20audit%20of%20its%20information%20technology%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20had%20also%20come%20under%20fire%20for%20its%20backing%20from%20Ant%20Group%20Co.%2C%20the%20fintech%20leader%20founded%20by%20Jack%20Ma%2C%20particularly%20as%20domestic%20sentiment%20soured%20rapidly%20on%20Chinese%20firms.%20Last%20year%2C%20Sharma%20orchestrated%20a%20deal%20under%20which%20he%20acquired%20Paytm%20shares%20from%20Ant%20in%20return%20for%20convertibles%2C%20effectively%20diminishing%20the%20Chinese%20firm's%20influence%20and%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20latest%20order%20worsens%20the%20bank's%20woes%20with%20the%20regulator%20making%20scathing%20observations%20about%20its%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20comprehensive%20system%20audit%20report%20and%20subsequent%20compliance%20validation%20report%20of%20the%20external%20auditors%20revealed%20persistent%20non-compliances%20and%20continued%20material%20supervisory%20concerns%20in%20the%20bank%2C%20warranting%20further%20supervisory%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20RBI%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20said%20the%20bank%20won't%20be%20allowed%20to%20take%20any%20further%20deposits%20or%20conduct%20credit%20transactions%20or%20carry%20out%20top-ups%20on%20any%20customer%20accounts%2C%20prepaid%20instruments%2C%20wallets%2C%20cards%20for%20paying%20road%20tolls%20after%20Feb%2029.%20Also%2C%20special%20purpose%20accounts%20of%20parent%20firm%20One97%20Communications%20and%20Paytm%20Payments%20Services%20Ltd.%20used%20to%20make%20settlements%20are%20to%20be%20terminated%20no%20later%20than%20Feb.%2029%2C%20the%20RBI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20response%2C%20Paytm%20said%20it%20was%20taking%20urgent%20steps%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20RBI's%20order%20and%20was%20working%20with%20the%20banking%20regulator%20to%20assuage%20concerns%20as%20early%20as%20possible.%20Going%20forward%2C%20One97%20won't%20work%20with%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%2C%20and%20will%20expand%20its%20financial%20and%20payments%20services%20through%20its%20partnerships%20with%20other%20banks%2C%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20filing%20to%20stock%20exchanges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne97's%20other%20businesses%20such%20as%20loan%20and%20insurance%20distribution%20as%20well%20as%20equity%20broking%2C%20which%20are%20not%20related%20to%20the%20payments%20bank%2C%20will%20likely%20remain%20unaffected%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20has%20been%20taking%20forceful%20action%20in%20recent%20months%20to%20clamp%20down%20on%20risks%20in%20the%20financial%20sector%2C%20hitting%20affected%20stocks.%20At%20the%20end%20of%20last%20year%2C%20it%20barred%20lenders%20from%20investing%20in%20alternative%20investment%20funds%20that%20hold%20stakes%20in%20their%20borrowers%20to%20prevent%20an%20unstable%20build%20up%20of%20assets.%20Before%20that%2C%20it%20imposed%20stricter%20rules%20to%20stem%20the%20relentless%20rise%20in%20risky%20consumer%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERBI%20Governor%20Shaktikanta%20Das%20said%20last%20month%20that%20India's%20financial%20sector%20needs%20to%20remain%20more%20watchful%20on%20risk%20management.%20He%20said%20some%20banks%20and%20non-bank%20financial%20companies%20didn't%20have%20the%20bandwidth%20to%20manage%20a%20surge%20in%20loans%20approved%20by%20algorithm%20models%20used%20by%20the%20financial%20institutions.%20RBI%20will%20guard%20against%20any%20sense%20of%20complacency%20and%20is%20committed%20to%20safeguard%20trust%20in%20the%20Indian%20financial%20sector%2C%20according%20to%20Das.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20key%20impact%20of%20RBI's%20latest%20order%20can%20be%20on%20Paytm's%20lending%20business%20if%20partners%20limit%20business%20due%20to%20operational%20and%20governance%20risks%2C%20according%20to%20Jefferies%20and%20Macquarie%20analysts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bigger%20issue%20is%20Paytm%20has%20not%20been%20on%20the%20good%20books%20of%20the%20regulator%20and%20going%20forward%2C%20their%20lending%20partners%20also%20could%20possibly%20re-look%20at%20the%20relationships%