%20developing%20a%20school%20before.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20Viren%20Joshi%2C%20the%20president%20of%20the%20school%2C%20approached%20me%20to%20have%20a%20look%2C%20I%20was%20very%20honoured.%20I%20was%20excited%20to%20get%20to%20the%20school%20and%20start%20the%20designing%20process%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20idea%20behind%20the%20school%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20an%20existing%20building%20but%20was%20in%20a%20bad%20condition.%20It%20was%20a%20school%20for%20underprivileged%20children%20with%20visual%20impairment.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20two%20buildings%20%E2%80%94%20one%20was%20a%20hostel%20facility%20and%20the%20other%20one%20was%20the%20school.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20each%20room%2C%20twelve%20to%20fifteen%20students%20were%20living%20in%20bunk%20beds.%20Consequently%2C%20a%20decision%20was%20made%20to%20construct%20a%20new%20academic%20building%20and%20convert%20the%20existing%20structure%20entirely%20into%20a%20hostel%20facility.%20This%20would%20allow%20for%20redistribution%20of%20students%20across%20the%20ground%20and%20first%20floors%2C%20while%20providing%20them%20with%20more%20comfortable%20and%20improved%20living%20spaces.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20School%20for%20The%20Blind%20and%20Visually%20Impaired%20is%20located%20in%20Gandhinagar%2C%20Gujarat.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fschool-3-1706623026-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2