y%2C%20the%20routine%20stopped.%20The%20COVID%20pandemic%20had%20extended%20its%20reach%20to%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReimagining%20old-school%20classics%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20disheartening%20for%20the%20boys%20to%20watch%20their%20father%2C%20who%20loved%20the%20dairy%2C%20now%20sit%20at%20home.%20Business%20was%20at%20an%20all-time%20low.%20And%20somewhere%2C%20Harshit%20felt%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331406%2Fwrestler-parmanand-jain-started-mahaveer-rabri-bhandar-became-iconic-eatery-of-jaipur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20legacy%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20going%20to%20falter%20unless%20they%20stepped%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPistabarfi%20was%20born%20out%20of%20a%20quest%20to%20save%20a%20heirloom%20business.%20Though%20testing%20new%20waters%2C%20the%20brothers%20say%20there%20was%20absolutely%20no%20friction.%20Tanay%20brought%20his%20expertise%20in%20dealing%20with%20the%20logistics%2C%20while%20Harshit%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20the%20creative%20aspect%20of%20the%20venture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20was%20for%20the%20family%20to%20continue%20selling%20%3Cem%3Emithai%3C%2Fem%3E%20through%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F223780%2Fmumbai-entrepreneur-harsh-kedia-diabetic-chef-guilt-free-desserts-inspiring-india-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecloud%20kitchen%20approach%3C%2Fa%3E%20until%20Janta%20Dairy%20was%20ready%20to%20reopen.%20The%20first%20two%20years%20were%20not%20so%20much%20about%20sales%20but%20building%20a%20brand%20voice%2C%20says%20Tanay.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F1641993686173_11zon-1706614852.jpg%5C%22