l%20to%20check%20the%20desertification%20tendencies%20of%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBamboo%20is%20one%20of%20the%20fastest%20growing%20plant%20species.%20It%20is%20also%20a%20low-cost%20method%20to%20absorb%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20carbon.%20It%20produces%20about%2035%20percent%20more%20oxygen%20than%20any%20other%20plant%20creating%20an%20oxygen%20park%20in%20nature%20for%20future%20generations.%20It%20can%20boost%20the%20moisture%20content%20and%20the%20organic%20carbon%20in%20the%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20mentions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20its%20low-cost%20carbon%20sequestration%20property%2C%20Johnson%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CBamboo%20is%20going%20to%20be%20the%20next%20timber%20in%20the%20world%20because%20of%20its%20versatile%20usage.%20It%20is%20mainly%20used%20in%20construction%20like%20flooring%20and%20scaffolding%2C%20furniture%20making%2C%20as%20edible%20food%2C%20biofuel%2C%20fabrics%2C%20cloth%2C%20and%20paper-making.%20It%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F334919%2Fchiblu-idlis-in-bamboo-bengaluru-babu-hotel-halaguru-village-in-karnataka%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emedicinally%20useful%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20has%20religious%20and%20ornamental%20value.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-4-1706104470.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Johnson%20says%20bamboo%20produces%20about%2035%20percent%20more%20oxygen%20than%20any%20other%20plant.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-4-1706104470.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FBamboo-4-1706104470-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads