%3C%2Fa%3Efrom%202021%20reveal%20that%20the%20country%20generates%20approximately%2062%20tonnes%20of%20Municipal%20Solid%20Waste%20(MSW)%20annually.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20this%20total%2C%2080%20percent%20is%20collected%2C%20but%20only%2022-28%20percent%20undergoes%20recycling.%20The%20remaining%20waste%20is%20deposited%20in%20landfills%2C%20contributing%20to%20additional%20environmental%20challenges.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffactly.in%2Freview-municipal-solid-waste-generated-in-india-set-to-increase-7-times-in-the-next-30-years%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCurrently%252C%2520as%2520per%2520government%2520estimates%2C%252C%2520wood%252C%2520glass%252C%2520etc.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReports%20%3C%2Fa%3Esuggest%20that%20the%20percentage%20of%20MSW%20is%20anticipated%20to%20surge%20by%20sevenfold%20in%20the%20next%20decade%2C%20exacerbating%20the%20issue%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20staggering%20figures%20underscore%20the%20critical%20problem%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332607%2Fkerala-pharma-scientist-kenterra-low-cost-solution-waste-management-compost-apartment-complex%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewaste%20segregation%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20micro%20level.%20Records%20indicate%20that%20a%20mere%2030%20percent%20of%20waste%20undergoes%20proper%20segregation%2C%20leading%20to%20recyclable%20materials%20like%20plastic%20being%20wrongly%20disposed%20of%20in%20landfills%2C%20where%20they%20contribute%20to%20environmental%20degradation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20I%20believe%20is%20that%20people%20need%20some%20kind%20of%20incentive%20to%20do%20something.%20So%20I%20decided%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20concept%20where%20people%20get%20a%20reward%20for%20segregating%20their%20waste%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhishek%20Agarwal%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Goodeebag.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoodeebag%2C%20a%20Hyderabad-based%20waste%20management%20company%2C%20collects%20your%20segregated%20waste%20from%20your%20doorstep%20and%20provides%20reward%20points%20in%20return.%20Users%20can%20redeem%20these%20reward%20points%20to%20purchase%20groceries%20from%20the%20Goodeebag%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20icing%20on%20the%20top%3F%20All%20these%20services%20are%20free%20of%20cost!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOne%20man%E2%80%99s%20waste%20is%20another%E2%80%99s%20treasure%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20from%20a%20typical%20Marwari%20family%2C%20Abhishek%20claims%20that%20business%20is%20in%20his%20blood.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20entire%20family%20is%20full%20of%20successful%20businessmen%20in%20various%20fields%2C%20so%20for%20me%2C%20I%20had%20always%20known%20that%20entrepreneurship%20was%20my%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-8-1706017585.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20company%20and%20recycled%20over%2089%2C164%20kg%20of%20waste%20so%20far.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-8-1706017585.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-8-1706017585-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-8-1706017585-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-8-1706017585-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-8-1706017585-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339595%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20company%20and%20recycled%20over%2089%2C164%20kg%20of%20waste%20so%20far.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Goodeebag%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20Gooedeebag%2C%20Abhishek%20had%20started%20a%20logistics%20company.%20%E2%80%9CAlthough%20the%20business%20was%20running%20smoothly%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20something%20more%20in%20my%20life.%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20that%20gives%20back%20to%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20span%20of%2013%20years%2C%20I%20had%20expanded%20the%20business%20to%20many%20cities%20and%20had%20a%20fleet%20of%20vehicles%20too.%20However%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20sell%20the%20company%20and%20find%20something%20that%20aligns%20with%20what%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Abhishek%20was%20searching%20for%20his%20calling%2C%20he%20realised%20a%20persistent%20problem.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20that%20helps%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312674%2Fanish-malpani-quit-us-job-to-launch-ashaya-recycles-multi-layered-plastic-into-sunglasses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20environment%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20biggest%20problem%20I%20came%20across%20was%20waste.%20I%20narrowed%20it%20down%20to%20the%20micro%20level%20and%20found%20out%20that%20most%20households%20were%20either%20not%20aware%20of%20proper%20waste%20segregation%20or%20were%20too%20busy%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20solve%20the%20problem%20of%20landfills%20and%20waste%20remaining%20unrecycled%2C%20Abhishek%20opines%20that%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20find%20the%20core%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20I%20had%20recognised%20the%20issue%2C%20a%20small%20idea%20sprung%20into%20my%20head.%20I%20started%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20where%20I%20invited%20people%20to%20segregate%20their%20waste%20and%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20me%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20goody%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20it%20worked!%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20showed%20so%20much%20interest%20and%20were%20willing%20to%20do%20it%20for%20a%20reward.%20It%20was%20a%20new%20and%20interesting%20concept%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20sign%20enough%20and%20Abhishek%20decided%20to%20expand%20on%20this%20idea.%20%E2%80%9CA%20small%20family%20of%20people%2C%20everyday%20400%20to%20500%20gm%20of%20plastic%20is%20generated%20at%20home.%20There%20are%20no%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310812%2Fmukul-chhabra-scrapuncle-delhi-startup-collects-recycles-scrap-wins-lakhs-shark-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20scrap%20dealers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20will%20take%20that%20amount%20of%20plastic.%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20was%20a%20problem%20with%20many%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20push%20people%20to%20make%20segregating%20waste%20a%20habit%20and%20part%20of%20their%20daily%20routine%2C%20Abhishek%20decided%20to%20give%20them%20an%20incentive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20how%20the%20idea%20behind%20Goodeebag%20came%20about%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-9-1706017651.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20Agarwal%2C%20Founder%20of%20Goodeebag.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-9-1706017651.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-9-1706017651-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-9-1706017651-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-9-1706017651-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2Fycharit-9-1706017651-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339597%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20Agarwal%2C%20Founder%20of%20Goodeebag.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Goodeebag%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Something%20for%20Nothing%E2%80%99%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20passion%20for%20me%20more%20than%20anything%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20recalling%20how%20his%20friends%20and%20family%20reacted%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20start%20the%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20not%20as%20excited%20as%20I%20was.%20I%20had%20an%20existing%20business%20that%20was%20doing%20well%20and%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20switch.%20They%20would%20think%20that%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20it%20is%20%3Cem%3E%E2%80%98Kabaad%20ka%20business%E2%80%99%3C%2Fem%3E%20(scrap%20business).%20It%20was%20my%20passion%20towards%20nature%20conservation%20that%20kept%20me%20going%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20feels%20that%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20responsibility%20to%20manage%20waste%20but%20ours%20too.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20concept%20of%20giving%20away%20rewards%20comes%20from%20my%20basic%20understanding%20of%20human%20nature.%20We%20all%20love%20free%20stuff%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20we%3F%20So%20the%20reward%20system%20has%20worked%20perfectly%20for%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20how%20his%20company%20works%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20we%20have%20an%20app%20which%20a%20consumer%20downloads.%20They%20segregate%20their%20waste%20and%20schedule%20a%20visit%20from%20the%20app.%20Our%20collection%20executive%20comes%20and%20picks%20up%20their%20waste.%20The%20consumer%20can%20go%20to%20the%20application%20and%20collect%20their%20reward%20points.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20has%20a%20variety%20of%20products%20that%20consumers%20can%20buy.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20usually%20have%20household%20stuff%20and%20groceries%20which%20the%20consumers%20can%20buy%20for%20free.%20We%20deliver%20them%20to%20their%20homes%20within%2072%20hours%20without%20a%20delivery%20charge.%20So%20basically%2C%20you%20get%20something%20for%20nothing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20limit%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F311633%2Fruhani-verma-built-indias-first-carbon-negative-recyclable-public-toilet-amritsar-airport%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eamount%20of%20waste%20%3C%2Fa%3Eyou%20need%20to%20be%20picked%20up%2C%20and%20the%20rewards%20are%20based%20on%20the%20weight%20of%20the%20waste%20collected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20waste%20is%20collected%2C%20Abhishek%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%20comes%20to%20our%20storage%20units%20where%20it%20is%20segregated%20again.%20The%20dry%20waste%20collected%20is%20segregated%20into%2040%20categories%20including%20paper%2C%20cardboard%2C%20textile%20plastic%2C%20wires%2C%20metals%20etc.%20Most%20of%20the%20waste%20is%20plastic%20waste%20which%20goes%20to%20a%20factory%20where%20it%20is%20converted%20into%20tiles.%20We%20have%20collaboration%20with%20recyclers%20where%20waste%20goes%20to%20and%20apparel%20companies%20that%20need%20waste%20materials%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzdZCvlvXE6%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC