oreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F254694%2Fblack-fungus-covid-19-coronavirus-infection-dr-vikas-maurya-pulmonologist-lung-mortality-rate-medicines-steroids-oxygen-diabetes-co-morbidities-information-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMucormycosis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20rare%20but%20deadly%20infection%20also%20known%20as%20Black%20Fungus.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20infection%20has%20been%20reported%20in%20patients%20suffering%20from%20uncontrolled%20diabetes%2C%20HIV%2FAIDS%2C%20and%20other%20medical%20conditions%20up%20to%20the%20very%20recent%20COVID-19.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fbooks%2FNBK544364%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethis%20description%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Pure%20and%20Applied%20Microbiology%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%201885%2C%20the%20German%20pathologist%20Paltauf%2C%20reported%20the%20first%20case%20of%20Mucormycosis%20and%20described%20it%20as%20Mycosis%20Mucorina.%20During%20%5Bthe%5D%201980s%20and%201990s%20Mucormycosis%20was%20increasingly%20seen%20among%20immunocompromised%20individuals.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20The%20term%20Mucormycosis%2C%20however%2C%20was%20first%20coined%20by%20American%20pathologist%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjamanetwork.com%2Fjournals%2Fjama%2Farticle-abstract%2F320257%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERD%20Baker%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%201950s.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20at%20IIT-M%20has%20joined%20hands%20with%20ZorioX%20Innovation%20Labs%2C%20a%20Chennai-based%20medical%20equipment%20manufacturing%20startup%2C%20to%20organise%20around%2065%20implants%20for%20patients%20from%20economically-weaker%20sections.%20This%20initiative%20is%20based%20on%20metal%203D%20printing%20or%20additive%20manufacturing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20sits%20down%20with%20the%20minds%20behind%20this%20thoughtful%20venture%20to%20understand%20its%20scope%20in%20depth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDangers%20of%20the%20deadly%20black%20fungus%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20an%20August%202023%20paper%20published%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC10168193%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJournal%20of%20Medical%20Mycology%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Gregoire%20Pasquier%2C%20%E2%80%9CMucormycosis%20is%20a%20rare%20opportunistic%20infection%20caused%20by%20a%20filamentous%20fungus%20belonging%20to%20the%20Mucorales%20order%E2%80%A6The%20diagnosis%20is%20difficult%20and%20consequently%2C%20it%20is%20often%20delayed%2C%20resulting%20in%20high%20lethality%20despite%20appropriate%20antifungal%20and%20surgical%20treatment.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20second%20wave%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F267348%2Fomicron-india-covid-update-karnataka-genome-surveillance-committee%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID-19%3C%2Fa%3E%20pandemic%20in%202021%20led%20to%20an%20upsurge%20in%20mucormycosis%20cases%20known%20as%20Covid-19-associated%20mucormycosis%20or%20CAM.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndian%20media%2C%20based%20on%20statements%20by%20members%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20reported%2011%2C717%20CAM%20cases%20on%20May%2025%2C%2028%2C252%20CAM%20cases%20on%20June%207%2C%2045%2C274%20CAM%20cases%20(including%204332%20deaths)%20on%20July%2020%2C%20and%2051%2C775%20CAM%20cases%20on%20November%2029%2C%202021%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Pasquier.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20precise%20data%20were%20available%20because%20on%20May%2020%2C%202021%2C%20mucormycosis%20became%20a%20notifiable%20disease%20under%20the%20Epidemic%20Diseases%20Act%201897.%20Before%20this%20epidemic%2C%20mucormycosis%20was%20considered%20a%20rare%20opportunistic%20infection%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20particularly%20devastating%20effect%20of%20this%20disease%20is%20the%20loss%20of%20facial%20features%20which%20can%20have%20a%20debilitating%20effect%20on%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20mental%20health.%20The%20fungus%20responsible%20for%20mucormycosis%20can%20invade%20the%20tissues%20of%20the%20face%2C%20causing%20necrosis%20and%20disfigurement.%20In%20severe%20cases%2C%20patients%20can%20lose%20their%20eyes%2C%20nose%2C%20or%20even%20their%20entire%20face.%20The%20loss%20of%20these%20vital%20organs%20can%20seriously%20impact%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20perform%20basic%20functions%20like%20breathing%2C%20eating%2C%20and%20communicating.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-Image-4-1706014757.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Team%20behind%20face%20implants%20for%20black%20fungus%20patients%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-Image-4-1706014757.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-Image-4-1706014757-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-Image-4-1706014757-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-Image-4-1706014757-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-Image-4-1706014757-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339557%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Murugaiyan%20Amirthalingam%20(L)%20of%20IIT%20Madras%20with%20the%20team%20that%20works%20on%203D-printed%20face%20implants%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESolutions%20found%20in%203D%20implants%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20viable%20solution%20is%20reconstructive%20surgery%20for%20patients%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20facial%20features%20due%20to%20this%20debilitating%20disease.%20As%20a%20detailed%20press%20release%20issued%20by%20IIT-M%20last%20month%20states%2C%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20procedures%20involve%20the%20reconstruction%20of%20the%20nose%2C%20eyes%2C%20and%20other%20facial%20structures%20using%20a%20variety%20of%20techniques%2C%20such%20as%20skin%20grafts%2C%20tissue%20expansion%2C%20and%20microvascular%20surgery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThese%20procedures%20can%20help%20restore%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20appearance%20and%20function%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20lead%20a%20more%20normal%20life.%20However%2C%20patient-specific%20implants%20and%20procedures%20are%20expensive%2C%20rendering%20them%20inaccessible%20for%20people%20from%20weaker%20sections%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20release%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Dr%20Karthik%20Balaji%2C%20a%20maxillofacial%20surgeon%20and%20CEO%20of%20ZorioX%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20college%2C%20I%20delved%20into%20exploring%20advanced%20techniques%20for%20replacing%20facial%20structures.%20Witnessing%20the%20complexities%20and%20limitations%20of%20existing%20methods%20fueled%20my%20determination%20to%20find%20a%20more%20efficient%20and%20patient-friendly%20approach.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20integration%20of%203D%20printing%20technology%20emerged%20as%20a%20promising%20solution%2C%20offering%20precise%20and%20customised%20implants%20that%20streamline%20the%20reconstruction%20process%2C%20reduce%20surgical%20time%2C%20and%20alleviate%20the%20need%20for%20multiple%20procedures.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20process%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20conventional%20reconstructive%20surgery%2C%20we%20take%20bones%20from%20legs%2C%20hips%2C%20or%20ribs%20and%20reconstruct%20the%20face.%20This%20has%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20a%20microvascular%20surgery%20which%20can%20take%20as%20long%20as%2018%20hours.%20To%20fix%20these%20bones%2C%20we%20use%20a%20plate%20that%20is%20going%20inside%20the%20body.%20As%20a%20medical%20researcher%2C%20I%20was%20working%20on%20finding%20ways%20to%20develop%20a%20plate%20in%20the%20shape%20of%20the%20facial%20bone%2C%20fix%20the%20problem%2C%20and%20avoid%20microvascular%20surgery%2C%20thus%20reducing%20the%20time%20taken%20for%20surgery.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThankfully%2C%203D-printing%20technology%20came%20to%20be.%20With%20the%20introduction%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318820%2Fiit-graduates-micob-ahmedabad-startup-uses-3d-printing-to-build-walls-houses-bunkers%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E3D-printing%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dr%20Balaji%20claims%20that%20they%20have%20reduced%20surgical%20time%20from%2018%20hours%20to%202%20hours.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20use%20bones%20from%20another%20part%20of%20the%20body%20now.%20Instead%2C%20we%20will%20use%20this%20titanium%203D-printed%20implant%20which%20is%20biocompatible.%20Unlike%20conventional%20reconstructive%20surgery%2C%20which%20allows%20patients%20to%20eat%20only%20two%20years%20after%2C%20followed%20by%20another%20surgery%3B%20in%20employing%203D-printed%20implants%2C%20we%20only%20need%20one%20surgery%20and%20the%20patient%20can%20eat%20within%20a%20month.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20these%203D-printed%20implants%20allow%20patients%20to%20return%20to%20normal%20life%20a%20lot%20sooner%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201165px)%20100vw%2C%201165px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-M-Black-Fungus-1706015429.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221165%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Solutions%20to%20black%20fungus%20in%20face%20implants%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-M-Black-Fungus-1706015429.jpg%201165w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-M-Black-Fungus-1706015429-300x201.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-M-Black-Fungus-1706015429-500x335.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-M-Black-Fungus-1706015429-768x514.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-M-Black-Fungus-1706015429-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339567%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22780%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Murugaiyan%20Amirthalingam%20(L)%20and%20a%20team%20member%20with%20a%203D-printed%20face%20implant%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20differences%20between%20conventional%20reconstructive%20surgery%20and%20employing%20IIT-M%E2%80%99s%203D-printed%20customised%20implants%20lie%20in%20precision%2C%20efficiency%2C%20and%20the%20overall%20patient%20experience.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Balaji%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20conventional%20reconstructive%20surgery%2C%20the%20process%20often%20starts%20from%20surgical%20removal%20of%20facial%20bones%20and%20reconstruction%20of%20those%20defects%20with%20the%20use%20of%20bone%20grafting%20techniques%3B%20this%20adds%20complexity%20to%20the%20procedure%20and%20is%20highly%20technique-sensitive.%20Over%20these%20grafts%2C%20conventionally%20made%20implants%20must%20be%20placed%20and%20that%20incurs%20additional%20burden%20to%20the%20patient%20barring%20the%20procedure.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Murugaiyan%20Amirthalingam%2C%20associate%20professor%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Metallurgical%20and%20Materials%20Engineering%2C%20IIT-Madras%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9COn%20the%20contrary%2C%20our%203D-printed%20custom%20implants%20offer%20a%20more%20tailored%20and%20precise%20solution.%20The%20implants%20are%20created%20based%20on%20detailed%20scans%20of%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20anatomy%20ensuring%20an%20exact%20fit%2C%20post-removal%20of%20facial%20bones.%20This%20level%20of%20customisation%20not%20only%20enhances%20the%20aesthetic%20outcome%20but%20also%20contributes%20to%20a%20more%20efficient%20surgical%20process.%20The%20use%20of%203D%20printing%20technology%20allows%20for%20intricate%20designs%20that%20match%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20unique%20facial%20features%2C%20resulting%20in%20improved%20functionality.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Dr%20Amirthalingam%20goes%20on%20to%20explain%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20motivation%20behind%20developing%203D-printed%20face%20implants%20stemmed%20from%20the%20challenges%20faced%20in%20conventional%20techniques%20of%20facial%20reconstruction.%20We%20have%20developed%20a%20methodology%20for%20the%20use%20of%203D%20printing%20to%20design%20and%20manufacture%20unique%20custom-designed%20components%20for%20various%20biomedical%20and%20engineering%20applications.%20When%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20arose%20and%20the%20number%20of%20black%20fungus%20cases%20increased%2C%20surgeons%20approached%20us%20with%20possible%20solutions%20to%20develop%20patient-specific%20implants%20using%203D%20printing.%20We%20could%20immediately%20help%20them%20as%20the%20technology%20was%20already%20developed%20in%20our%20lab.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Dr%20Balaji%20and%20his%20colleagues%20started%20these%20procedures%20initially%2C%20they%20had%20to%20import%20the%20%5B3D-printed%5D%20implants%20from%20the%20Netherlands%20or%20the%20United%20States.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20cost%20of%20a%20single%20implant%20was%20around%20Rs%2024%20lakh.%20Working%20with%20various%20engineering%20institutions%2C%20we%20developed%20the%20requisite%20facilities%20and%20software%20to%20develop%20these%20implants%2C%20and%20IIT-Madras%20began%20helping%20us%20manufacture%20them.%20After%20bringing%20all%20the%20necessary%20facilities%20to%20India%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20implant%20fell%20from%20Rs%2024%20lakh%20to%20Rs%208%20lakh%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20720px)%20100vw%2C%20720px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Karthik-Balaji-1706015088.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black%20Fungus%20Innovation%20for%20face%20implants%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Karthik-Balaji-1706015088.jpg%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Karthik-Balaji-1706015088-300x184.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Karthik-Balaji-1706015088-500x307.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Karthik-Balaji-1706015088-150x92.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339561%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22442%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Karthik%20Balaji%20(R)%20of%20Zoriox%20Innovation%20Lab%20presenting%20an%20MOU%20with%20IIT%20Madras%20to%20develop%203D-printed%20face%20implants%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20does%20it%20work%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Amirthalingam%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CUsing%20unique%20in-house%20algorithms%2C%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20MRI%2FCT%20data%20is%20converted%20to%20printable%20CAD%20(computer-aided%20design)%20format%2C%20and%20custom%20implants%20are%20printed%20from%20medical-grade%20titanium%20using%20an%20indigenously-built%20laser%20powder%20bed%20facility%20in%20IIT-M.%20Extensive%20research%20activities%20are%20already%20being%20carried%20out%20in%20IIT%20Madras%20to%20commercialise%20this%20technology%20for%20printing%20patient-specific%20implants%20in%20stainless%20steel%2C%20Ti-6Al-4V%2C%20and%20Co-Cr-Mo%20alloys.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20IIT-Madras%20team%20can%20print%20the%20implant%20exactly%20to%20match%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20face.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20sets%20our%20approach%20apart%20is%20the%20ability%20to%20custom-design%20and%20print%20implants%20that%20precisely%20match%20a%20patient%E2%80%99s%20unique%20facial%20anatomy.%20Traditionally%2C%20reconstructive%20surgeons%20rely%20on%20pre-fabricated%20implants%2C%20which%20are%20akin%20to%20off-the-rack%20clothing.%20They%20might%20fit%20somewhat%2C%20but%20rarely%20perfectly%2C%20and%20also%20require%20additional%20alterations%20to%20patients%E2%80%99%20bone%20structures.%203D%20printing%20allows%20us%20to%20become%20bespoke%20craftsmen%2C%20crafting%20implants%20that%20are%20the%20exact%20size%20and%20shape%20of%20the%20missing%20facial%20bone.%20We%20use%20CT%20scans%20or%20MRIs%20of%20the%20patient%20directly%20to%20create%20a%20detailed%203D%20digital%20model%20of%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20face.%20Think%20of%20it%20as%20a%20high-resolution%20picture%2C%20but%20instead%20of%20just%20depth%2C%20it%20captures%20the%20intricate%20contours%20and%20internal%20structures%20of%20the%20missing%20bone%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENext%20comes%20the%20magic%20of%20CAD.%20%E2%80%9COur%20skilled%20research%20scholars%20and%20Zoriox%20team%20take%20the%20medical%20image%20data%20and%2C%20using%20specialised%20algorithms%2C%20transform%20it%20into%20a%20digital%20blueprint%20for%20the%20implant.%20This%20blueprint%2C%20called%20a%20CAD%20STL%20(stereolithography)%20file%2C%20essentially%20tells%20the%203D%20printer%20exactly%20how%20to%20build%20the%20implant%2C%20layer%20by%20layer%2C%20mimicking%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20unique%20facial%20features%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20CAD%20STL%20file%20is%20ready%2C%20the%203D%20printer%20takes%20centre%20stage.%20Imagine%20a%20high-tech%20sculpting%20machine%20that%20uses%20medical-grade%20titanium%20powder%20to%20meticulously%20build%20the%20implant%2C%20following%20the%20precise%20instructions%20in%20the%20CAD%20STL%20file.%20Layer%20by%20layer%2C%20the%20missing%20bone%20structure%20comes%20to%20life%2C%20perfectly%20customised%20for%20the%20patient%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20significant%20hurdle%20was%20the%20initial%20capital%20expenditure%20cost%20associated%20with%20acquiring%20and%20implementing%203D%20printing%20technology.%20Another%20challenge%20involved%20ensuring%20a%20reliable%20supply%20of%20titanium%2C%20the%20chosen%20material%20for%20the%20implants.%20Most%20medical%20grade%203D-printable%20titanium%20powders%20were%20imported%20which%20increased%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20implants%20manyfold.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20then%20collaborated%20with%20an%20Indian%20supplier%20to%20help%20produce%20medical-grade%20titanium%20powders.%20Extensive%20testing%20was%20carried%20out%20in%20our%20lab%20to%20qualify%20the%20raw%20material%20produced%20by%20the%20Indian%20vendor%20for%20medical%20implant%20production%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Dr%20Amirthalingam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSubsequently%2C%20careful%20resource%20planning%20helped%20secure%20a%20consistent%20procurement%20of%20high-quality%2C%20biocompatible%20titanium%20suitable%20for%20facial%20implants.%20Establishing%20accurate%20parameters%20for%203D%20printing%20was%20a%20crucial%20step%20in%20achieving%20the%20desired%20precision.%20Our%20team%20of%20experts%20in%20additive%20manufacturing%20fine-tuned%20the%20printing%20parameters%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20implants%20met%20stringent%20quality%20standards%20and%20conformed%20precisely%20to%20the%20patient%E2%80%99s%20anatomy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20Dr%20Balaji%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20project%20like%20this%20is%20complete%20without%20the%20invaluable%20input%20of%20the%20surgeons.%20Their%20extensive%20experience%20and%20meticulous%20feedback%20guided%20every%20step%20of%20the%20process%2C%20from%20initial%20design%20to%20post-operative%20care.%20This%20synergistic%20collaboration%20between%20engineers%2C%20designers%2C%20and%20surgeons%20was%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20our%20success.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-3D-printed-Face-Implant-Feature-2-1706014919.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Black%20Fungus%20patients%20need%203D-printed%20face%20implants%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-3D-printed-Face-Implant-Feature-2-1706014919.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-3D-printed-Face-Implant-Feature-2-1706014919-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-3D-printed-Face-Implant-Feature-2-1706014919-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-3D-printed-Face-Implant-Feature-2-1706014919-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-3D-printed-Face-Implant-Feature-2-1706014919-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339560%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr.%20Murugaiyan%20Amirthalingam%20with%20the%203D%20Printer%20used%20for%20printing%20Face%20Implants%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%23Right2Face%20Initiative%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Amirthalingam%2C%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20collaboration%20with%20Zoriox%20began%20in%202021%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20shared%20vision%20to%20revolutionise%20maxillofacial%20%5Brelating%20to%20jaws%20and%20face%5D%20implants%20through%203D%20printing%20technology.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20he%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20our%20efforts%20focused%20on%20addressing%20key%20technical%20challenges%20associated%20with%20these%20novel%20implants%20namely%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESurface%20finish%3A%20Optimising%20the%20implant%20surface%20to%20promote%20tissue%20integration%20and%20minimise%20bacterial%20adhesion.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMachinability%3A%20Streamlining%20the%20manufacturing%20process%20for%20improved%20efficiency%20and%20cost%20reduction.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOsseointegration%3A%20Enhancing%20bone%20ingrowth%20and%20long-term%20implant%20stability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThrough%20collaborative%20research%20and%20development%2C%20they%20have%20made%20significant%20progress%20in%20these%20areas%2C%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20more%20reliable%20and%20functional%203D-printed%20implants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20their%20technical%20advancements%20matured%2C%20the%20focus%20shifted%20to%20broader%20societal%20impact.%20In%202023%2C%20the%20effort%20blossomed%20into%20the%20%3Cem%3ERight2Face%3C%2Fem%3E%20movement%2C%20driven%20by%20the%20following%20objectives%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ERaising%20awareness%3A%20Educating%20the%20public%20and%20medical%20community%20about%20the%20transformative%20potential%20of%203D-printed%20maxillofacial%20implants.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStandards%20development%3A%20Contributing%20to%20the%20establishment%20of%20robust%20quality%20and%20safety%20standards%20for%20these%20innovative%20implants.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMaterial%20exploration%3A%20Researching%20and%20developing%20new%20biocompatible%20materials%20that%20further%20enhance%20implant%20performance%20and%20affordability.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EImproved%20surgical%20outcomes%3A%20Collaborating%20with%20surgeons%20to%20refine%20surgical%20techniques%20and%20optimise%20patient%20outcomes%20with%203D-printed%20implants.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20save%20the%20lives%20of%20a%20patient%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20facial%20bones%20had%20to%20be%20removed.%20These%20patients%20are%20mostly%20breadwinners%20of%20the%20family%20and%20are%20now%20confined%20within%20four%20walls%20because%20of%20their%20facial%20deformity.%20The%20%23Right2face%20movement%20is%20aimed%20to%20help%20these%20needy%20patients%20in%20association%20with%20oral%20and%20maxillofacial%20surgeons%20to%20restore%20their%20faces%20and%20%E2%80%9Cgive%20them%20back%20their%20smile%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20720px)%20100vw%2C%20720px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Karthik-Balaji-1-1706015291.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22surgeons%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Karthik-Balaji-1-1706015291.jpg%20720w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Karthik-Balaji-1-1706015291-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Karthik-Balaji-1-1706015291-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FDr-Karthik-Balaji-1-1706015291-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-339563%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22540%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDr%20Karthik%20Balaji%20(R)%20presenting%20the%20%23Right2Face%20initiative%20in%20front%20of%20stalwarts%20of%20facial%20reconstruction%20surgery%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20press%20release%2C%20%E2%80%9CIIT%20Madras%20researchers%20are%20also%20identifying%20patients%20who%20cannot%20afford%20costly%20imported%20implants%20and%20giving%20these%20implants%20free%20of%20cost%20under%20the%20campaign%20called%20%23Right2Face.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20campaign%20was%20started%20by%20a%20group%20of%20maxillofacial%20surgeons%20including%20Dr%20Balaji%20last%20year.%20This%20group%20began%20by%20working%20with%20dental%20colleges%20where%20maxillofacial%20surgeries%20were%20done.%20They%20started%20working%20with%20state-funded%20dental%20colleges%20in%20Chennai%2C%20Cuddalore%2C%20and%20other%20such%20colleges%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20Telangana%20where%20they%20would%20find%20patients%20from%20economically%20weaker%20sections%20who%20needed%20these%20implants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIIT-Madras%20also%20came%20to%20help%20us%20with%20this%20initiative.%20We%20also%20worked%20with%20local%20nonprofits%20to%20raise%20some%20funds%20for%20these%20cases.%20It%20began%20with%20two%20or%20three%20cases%20and%20then%20IIT-Madras%20came%20in%20to%20help%20us%20with%20the%20implants.%20Before%20these%20procedures%2C%20we%20conduct%20one-on-one%20interviews%20with%20these%20patients%2C%20following%20which%20we%20obtain%20a%20letter%20from%20their%20doctors%20saying%20that%20they%20cannot%20afford%20these%20procedures%20and%20need%20help.%20After%20this%20letter%2C%20we%20check%20the%20ration%20card%20of%20the%20patient%20(if%20it%E2%80%99s%20available)%20to%20check%20their%20credibility%20and%20then%20we%20proceed%20with%20the%20implants%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Balaji.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAs%20a%20commercial%20entity%2C%20we%20have%20completed%20almost%20450%20implants.%20Under%20%23Right2Face%20where%20patients%20could%20not%20afford%20these%20procedures%2C%20we%20have%20done%2047%20cases%20and%20in%20about%2018%20cases%20or%20so%20patients%20were%20able%20to%20shell%20out%20some%20money%20but%20not%20enough%20to%20cover%20the%20procedure.%20Medical%20colleges%20are%20also%20helping%20us%20in%20waiving%20costs%20for%20patients%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20beneficiary%20of%20this%20initiative%20is%20a%2063-year-old%20vegetable%20vendor%20from%20Coimbatore%20who%20wishes%20to%20remain%20anonymous.%20Living%20with%20a%20wife%20and%20four%20daughters%2C%20things%20were%20okay%20till%20the%20first%20lockdown.%20Making%20matters%20worse%2C%20he%20tested%20positive%20for%20COVID-19%20and%20was%20infected%20by%20black%20fungus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20the%20lockdown%2C%20I%20was%20affected%20by%20black%20fungus%20because%20of%20which%20doctors%20had%20to%20remove%20my%20upper%20jaw.%20Wanting%20to%20resume%20work%20after%20the%20lockdown%2C%20I%20heard%20about%20facial%20reconstruction%20surgery%20and%20a%20doctor%20in%20Madurai%20who%20could%20perform%20it.%20When%20I%20reached%20Madurai%2C%20I%20approached%20Dr%20S%20Suraj%20(a%20maxillofacial%20surgeon)%20for%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Suraj%20then%20referred%20his%20case%20to%20the%20Zoriox%20team%2C%20and%20both%20sides%20agreed%20on%20developing%203D-printed%20patient-specific%20face%20implants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20%5Bthe%20procedure%5D%20was%20expensive%2C%20and%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20afford%20it.%20But%20under%20this%20%5B%23Right2Face%5D%20initiative%2C%20they%20supplied%20the%20implant%20to%20me%20%5Bfree%20of%20cost%5D.%20Dr%20Suraj%20did%20the%20surgery%2C%20placed%20the%20implant%20inside%2C%20and%20reconstructed%20my%20upper%20jaw%2C%20and%20I%20got%20my%20denture%20within%20one%20month.%20Now%2C%20I%20can%20eat%20properly%20and%20carry%20on%20with%20my%20everyday%20routine.%20I%E2%80%99d%20like%20to%20sincerely%20thank%20Dr%20Suraj%2C%20Zoriox%2C%20and%20IIT-Madras%20for%20helping%20me%2C%20%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20ahead%2C%20they%20are%20planning%20to%20help%20as%20many%20as%20patients%20who%20require%20these%20face%20implants.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COfficial%20data%20shows%20at%20least%2060%2C000%20people%20are%20suffering%20from%20post-black%20fungus%20facial%20deformities.%20We%20are%20approaching%20various%20corporations%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F123319%2Fcorporate-spend-three-sectors-csr%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECSR%20(Corporate%20Social%20Responsibility)%20funding%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20reaching%20out%20to%20other%20funding%20bodies.%20So%20far%2C%20we%20could%20manage%20using%20the%20existing%20funding%20from%20IIT%20Madras%20and%20CSR%20in-kind%20contributions%20from%20the%20hospitals.%20However%2C%20through%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20we%20are%20reaching%20out%20to%20your%20readers%20to%20support%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Balaji.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20IIT-Madras%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fdr-karthik-balaji-776731204%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr%20Karthik%20Balaji%2FLinkedIn%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(If%20you%20want%20to%20contribute%20to%20this%20initiative%2C%20please%20click%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjoyofgiving.alumni.iitm.ac.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706018426000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2FIIT-Madras-Black-Fungus-Image-4-1706014757.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D339541%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20collaboration%20between%20IIT%20Madras%20and%20Chennai-based%20startup%20ZorioX%20Innovation%20Labs%2C%20the%20%23Right2Face%20initiative%20aims%20to%20help%20poor%20patients%20with%20face%20implants%20developed%20using%20indigenous%203D-printing%20technology.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F339541%2Fiit-madras-chennai-startup-3d-printing-technology-free-face-implants-for-the-poor-patients%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Follow%20the%20Rhythm%20of%20Your%20Heart%E2%80%99%3A%2070-YO%20Woman%20Travels%20Solo%20to%2080%20Countries%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20everyone%20should%20follow%20the%20rhythm%20of%20their%20own%20heart%20and%20not%20the%20beat%20of%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%2070-year-old%20Neeru%20Saluja%20tells%20me.%20For%20the%20last%2014%20years%2C%20she%20has%20been%20the%20embodiment%20of%20this%20advice.%20When%20her%20husband%20and%20former%20travel%20buddy%20passed%20away%20in%202010%2C%20Neeru%20decided%20to%20continue%20their%20legacy%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F319083%2Fkannauj-perfumer-turns-ancestral-home-into-retreat-for-perfume-making-ancient-craft-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elove%20for%20adventure%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20staunch%20believer%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20life%20happens%20outside%20one%E2%80%99s%20comfort%20zone%2C%20this%20professor%2C%20wife%2C%20mother%20and%20now%20globetrotter%20has%20recently%20marked%20a%20milestone%20of%20having%2080%20countries%20under%20her%20belt.%20%E2%80%9CEighty%20and%20counting%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20reminds%20me%2C%20as%20she%20settles%20down%20in%20the%20living%20room%20of%20her%20Jaipur%20home%2C%20to%20recall%20her%20adventures%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20home%20seems%20like%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F314549%2Flong-drive-forest-roads-trips-mumbai-bengaluru-delhi-scenic-views-travel-plans-vacation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20map%20in%20itself%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20bedecked%20with%20souvenirs%20that%20Neeru%20has%20collected%20through%20her%20trips%2C%20right%20from%20the%20Galapagos%20Islands%20in%20the%20Pacific%20to%20the%20icy%20horizons%20of%20the%20Atlantic.%20A%20personal%20favourite%2C%20hands%20down%2C%20has%20to%20be%20the%20paintings%20she%20purchased%20from%20Cuban%20artists%2C%20she%20says.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20simply%20beautiful!%E2%80%9D%20These%20souvenirs%20are%20reminders%20of%20the%20adventures%20Neeru%20has%20had%20so%20far%2C%20and%20the%20empty%20spaces%20hold%20promise%20for%20what%E2%80%99s%20to%20come.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20question%20that%20begs%20to%20be%20asked%20is%20how%20does%20she%20do%20it%20at%2070!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%E2%80%99s%20your%20secret%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeeru%20laughs%2C%20suggesting%20there%20is%20no%20secret%2C%20but%20an%20interesting%20story%20that%20holds%20the%20reason%20behind%20her%20fascination%20for%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20her%20very%20first%20day%20of%20school%20when%20she%20was%20riding%20her%20bicycle%20and%20met%20with%20an%20accident%20that%20broke%20her%20left%20leg%2C%20Neeru%20says%2C%20ironically%20%E2%80%9Cit%20all%20started%20at%20that%20moment%E2%80%9D.%20Months%20of%20bedrest%20coupled%20with%20intense%20physiotherapy%20sessions%2C%20meant%20she%20was%20confined%20to%20a%20room%20while%20the%20other%20kids%20were%20at%20school.%20The%20absence%20of%20a%20TV%20or%20any%20form%20of%20entertainment%20compelled%20her%20to%20spend%20hours%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F29794